/*! \relates Parma_Polyhedra_Library::Octagonal_Shape<T>::Status
  Reads a keyword and its associated on/off flag from \p s.
  Returns <CODE>true</CODE> if the operation is successful,
  returns <CODE>false</CODE> otherwise.
